g.text: Your group on the EmSys course has a virtual device, called a
dotDevice that you can interact with. Your dot device can: speak,
making text appear above it; move +-10 in the x or y
direction; and change colour or size. Commands are issued
from your device via WebSockets to the centralised

text.tspan: EmSys lab server. To ensure that each group only interacts with
their dotDevice commands should contain the groups unique id, gid.
